title: NO FEE Contemporary 2 Bed 2 Bath in DUMBO!
posting_body: ['Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'Remarkable 2 Bed 2 Bath that offers lofty 10-foot ceilings, oversized grid-style windows with laminated sound attenuating glass, in-unit washer-dryer, dishwasher, stainless steel Bosch appliances, and beautiful contemporary finishes!', "This luxury building features 24-hour doorman, an expansive private park, indoor and outdoor resident's club, an unforgettable pool with resort deck, full size basketball court, cardio/ conditioning floor, spa, full-service cafe, media/ gaming lounge, children's playroom, pet spa, onsite parking with electric car charging stations.", 'Conveniently located near the F,A,C,2,3,A,C,R, and Fulton Ferry Landing.', 'Note: Listed price is net effective rent based on 1 month free on a 12-month lease.', 'Gross is $7,080.', 'LISTING #138555', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Pool', 'Garage', 'Subway', 'Laundry', 'Lounge', 'Common Outdoor Space', 'Receiving Room', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'High Ceilings', 'Light', 'NO FEE', 'Laundry In Unit', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'To view, call or text Sabrina Rosal at:', '201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>']
